logic.schemes.job

Class Job

  • java.lang.Object
    • logic.schemes.Scheme
      • logic.schemes.job.Job

  • @Entity(value="jobs")
public class Job
extends Scheme
    Base object to keep track of a job being done in a task. Holds one worker that is responsible for completing the job.
